research_municipality_step.notes: The elected officials for Bruceville-Eddy, TX, were identified from the city's official website and confirmed with other municipal directories and council meeting minutes. Linda Owens serves as Mayor. Graham McGruer holds the roles of Mayor Pro Tem and Councilman. Ricky Wiggins, Joyce McGlothlin, Justin Richardson, and Richard Prater serve as Council members. No specific ward, district, or precinct designations were found for these roles.
